title: Manufacturing Technical Support
description: Contract position with Dell at Boeing.
Resolve any hardware or software technical issues on over 5,000 desktop, laptop, and tablet computers on the Boeing manufacturing floors and flight lines in the Renton, Seattle, Tacoma areas.
Updating software, removing malicious software, replacing damaged hardware, reimaging OS, defragmenting hard drive, improving performance by removing unused files and user profiles.
Performing line walks to check all computers within our care to ensure all PCs are working optimally and to perform preventative maintenance.
